    {"id":"py_boxt","type":"text","x":56,"y":272,"width":528,"height":88,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e3a8a","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":11,"fontFamily":2,"text":"Language: Python 3.11+  |  Library: google-api-python-client  |  Auth: Google Service Account JSON\nPolls ALL 4 sheets in parallel every 30 seconds (configurable via POLL_INTERVAL env var)\nRow-level SHA-256 hash comparison — only writes to DB when data actually changes\nNormalises data: DD/MM/YYYY dates → YYYY-MM-DD  |  Title-cases all names\nGenerates demo_id: YYYYMMDD_teacherfirst_studentfirst  if not already in sheet\nOn NEW demo detected → automatically calls POST /api/wajeeha/process-demo (configurable OFF)\nRun as background daemon:  python scripts/watch_sheets.py  |  Full logs: logs/sheet_watcher.log","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"middle","containerId":null,"originalText":"Language: Python 3.11+  |  Library: google-api-python-client  |  Auth: Google Service Account JSON\nPolls ALL 4 sheets in parallel every 30 seconds (configurable via POLL_INTERVAL env var)\nRow-level SHA-256 hash comparison — only writes to DB when data actually changes\nNormalises data: DD/MM/YYYY dates → YYYY-MM-DD  |  Title-cases all names\nGenerates demo_id: YYYYMMDD_teacherfirst_studentfirst  if not already in sheet\nOn NEW demo detected → automatically calls POST /api/wajeeha/process-demo (configurable OFF)\nRun as background daemon:  python scripts/watch_sheets.py  |  Full logs: logs/sheet_watcher.log","lineHeight":1.45},

